416
00:23:40,280 --> 00:23:41,400
is going.

417
00:23:41,880 --> 00:23:42,280
Got it.

418
00:23:50,182 --> 00:23:54,262
(Dingshun Group)

419
00:24:00,120 --> 00:24:00,840
I'll say it again.

420
00:24:01,511 --> 00:24:03,177
If they want to spin off
the tech company

421
00:24:03,222 --> 00:24:04,155
