477
00:26:42,960 --> 00:26:44,480
Everything I promised you

478
00:26:44,760 --> 00:26:45,840
will be delivered.

479
00:26:47,120 --> 00:26:50,150
As of now, Dingshun has completed
the handover with Mr. Ye.

