491
00:27:14,600 --> 00:27:17,360
Mr. Ye has no ties with us.

492
00:27:18,080 --> 00:27:20,780
I personally agree with you.

493
00:27:21,760 --> 00:27:22,520
There's no future

494
00:27:22,955 --> 00:27:24,111
