plan to stay in Linshan?

501
00:27:43,160 --> 00:27:44,200
Hard to say.

502
00:27:44,760 --> 00:27:45,480
We'll see.

503
00:27:47,760 --> 00:27:48,280
Zhou,

504
00:27:49,280 --> 00:27:52,000
